## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee004-110">Se `Count` già pari alla capacità, la capacità dell'elenco viene raddoppiata automaticamente la riallocazione della matrice interna e copiando gli elementi esistenti nella nuova matrice prima che venga aggiunto il nuovo elemento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee004-110">If `Count` already equals the capacity, the capacity of list is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array and copying the existing elements to the new array before the new element is added.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee004-111">Se `Count` è minore della capacità, questo metodo è un'operazione di 0 (1).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee004-111">If `Count` is less than the capacity, this method is an 0(1) operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee004-112">Se la capacità deve essere incrementata per far posto al nuovo elemento, questo metodo diventa un'operazione 0(n), dove n è `Count`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee004-112">If the capacity needs to be increased to accommodate the new element, this method becomes an 0(n) operation, where n is `Count`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ee004-113">Il <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectCollection.Add%2A> metodo prevede solo <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaExternal> relativi tipi derivati e (<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaImport>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaInclude>, e <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaRedefine>) come parametri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee004-113">The <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectCollection.Add%2A> method expects only <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaExternal> and its derived types (<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaImport>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaInclude>, and <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaRedefine>) as parameters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ee004-114">Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrata l'aggiunta di uno schema incluso per la <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema.Includes%2A> raccolta di un oggetto esistente <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> oggetto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ee004-114">The following example illustrates adding an included schema to the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema.Includes%2A> collection of an existing <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Dim schema As XmlSchema = New XmlSchema()  
  
Dim textReader As XmlTextReader = New XmlTextReader("include.xsd")  
Dim includeSchema As XmlSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null)  
  
Dim include As XmlSchemaInclude = New XmlSchemaInclude()  
include.Schema = includeSchema;  
schema.Includes.Add(include);  
```  
  
```csharp  
XmlSchema schema = new XmlSchema();  
  
XmlTextReader textReader = new XmlTextReader("include.xsd");  
XmlSchema includeSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null);  
  
XmlSchemaInclude include = new XmlSchemaInclude();  
include.Schema = includeSchema;  
schema.Includes.Add(include);  
```
